ISLAMABAD, Nov 15 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Senator Shibli Faraz has expressed grief and sorrow over the sad demise of mother of Ameer Jamaat e Islami Senator Sirajul Haq.
In a message of condolence, he prayed Allah Almighty to rest the departed soul in eternal peace and grant courage to the bereaved family to bear the loss with fortitude.
